name: FIST
description: New FIST ($FIST) isn’t just another token — it’s a movement reborn from China’s legendary Pangu Community and now going global. Blending meme energy with deep-rooted crypto consensus, New FIST evolves from “personal-led” to “community-powered,” uniting global holders under one banner. Backed by the Binance ecosystem, it’s spreading fast across borders with a mission to prove that strong belief and shared vision can turn any meme into a worldwide force. Join the FIST family — where consensus meets culture!
